import basicState from './assets/icons8-full-image-96.png'

import Delete from './assets/icons8-trash-96.png'
import Review from './assets/writing.png'
import Add from './assets/outline_add_black_18.png'
import Setting from './assets/outline_settings_black_18.png'

export const images = {

    completed: checkState,
    update: Edit,
    delete: Delete,
    deleteAll: Delete,
    review : Review,
    add : Add,
    setting : Setting,
    search : Search,
